## Architecture
- Use Next.js App Router with Server Components by default.
- Only add `'use client'` for interactive UI.

## Styling
- Use Tailwind utilities.
- All colors, spacing, radii, shadows, and motion values come from tokens in `styles/tokens.css`.
- Avoid hardcoded styles.

## Motion
- Use Framer Motion for interactions and transitions.
- Motion tokens (`--dur-*`, `--ease`) must drive durations/easing.
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`.

## Validation
- Use Zod to validate external data.
- Infer types from Zod schemas whenever possible.

## Components
- Favor shadcn/ui primitives (Button, Card, Slider, Popover, etc.).
- Keep components small, composable, and accessible.

## Accessibility
- Always add `alt` text to images (or `alt=""` if decorative).
- Ensure keyboard focus and navigation works.
- Provide captions or transcripts for audio/video.

## Text
- Avoid apostrophes in text strings; use proper Unicode characters or alternatives.